1. Create an empty rust project
2. Add `rig-core`, `mcp-core` and other necessary dependencies to `Cargo.toml` (all latest version)
3. Copy and paste the `mcp-tool` example in `rig-core` into `main.rs`.
4. Run `cargo build`, the program fails to compile.

